#Overview
AlterPage is committed to protecting your privacy. This extension does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data or usage information to external servers. All data and settings used by the extension are stored locally on your device and are never shared.

#What Information Do We Collect?
None.
AlterPage does not collect or transmit any personal information, browsing history, cookies, IP addresses, or other identifiable data. The extension operates entirely within your browser and does not use any external analytics, tracking, or cloud-based storage.

#Local Storage
Any preferences or settings you configure within AlterPage are stored locally using your browser's extension storage system. This data is only accessible to you and the extension, and it remains on your device.

#Third-Party Services
AlterPage does not use or integrate with any third-party services or APIs that collect data.

#Changes to This Policy
If this privacy policy is updated in the future, any changes will be reflected on this page with a new effective date. However, we will never add data collection features without your clear knowledge and consent.
